| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4058 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aafc917f-4c72-5045-a358-4b3696aaad9f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
